{"tid":953971,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【心理學】總是抵抗不了誘惑?心理學家給你2個提高意志力的建議","createTime":"2018-12-24T10:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T15:27:29.000Z","uid":78029,"like":61,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"4a49d9e9cba865725c1770791c7278cb3f8387f5","tid":953971,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"大家好，又係小弟，小弟開咗個Youtube channel ，希望分享吓有趣小知識(心理學, 科學, 歷史, 甚至政治)<br />\n<br />\n今次講吓意志力, 由生理角度提升意志力的方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4cN0cWQtB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg4cN0cWQtB0&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=772f9811\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4cN0cWQtB0</a><br />\n<br />\n上次繼續講吓香港歷史, 聚焦去冷戰初期50年代的時勢點令到港英政府成立香港中文大學<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GfzPr1IcvA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0GfzPr1IcvA&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=75ace817\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GfzPr1IcvA</a><br />\n<br />\n上上次講吓點樣溫暖輕鬆提高別人對你的評價, 輕鬆獲取信任!<br />\n如有不足, 麻煩指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MwZzePErpMg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMwZzePErpMg&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ed40b41c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MwZzePErpMg</a><br />\n<br />\n上上上次講吓點樣用模仿輕鬆提高別人對你的好感,輕鬆獲取別人信任!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PxalLMq_gqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPxalLMq_gqw&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a27c1ba3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PxalLMq_gqw</a>"},{"pid":"4e9259bf5d246a7d9da1446a5554b633926d7b10","tid":953971,"uid":78029,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:06:51.000Z","msg":"呢次講吓教科書唔會教的香港歷史, 例如未開埠前有香港人幫英軍補給, 香港人唔係大中華史觀講到咁愛國 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3VyGBBak9Qs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3VyGBBak9Qs&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=cac4a94b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3VyGBBak9Qs</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集講吓新學到的知識有幾快會被遺忘,  又會遺忘幾多, 同埋我地有咩方法去減少遺忘, 將學到的知識由短期記憶轉化成長期記憶<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgHNy4VD0nEA&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3a30a378\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集講吓科學界點睇「世界上有無外星人? 如果有, 點解外星人無和我們接觸?」呢個問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3ob8lj7OM5Q&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d07b30ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集想講吓近年科學點睇「成年後腦袋係咪不再進步, 只會退化?」呢個問題, 從而介紹吓 我地可以點樣增加記憶力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D21byiVTSZhI&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=340a18c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓靈魂出竅/離體經驗係咩一回事, 科學界有無方法重現靈魂出竅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJhjpNvT-U4g&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e1b9c312\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓一D因為腦部受傷而成為奇才的人, 從而睇下未來科技有無可能將我地由普通人突然變成奇才<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeCEv3hfdco8&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d8dbab85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8</a><br />\n<br />\n第一集係由大腦科學, 心理學角度講吓愛情行為, 例如點解分手咁痛苦, 點解開始拍拖時會睇唔到對方缺點: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmgTq1gYCsZA&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=89cc9a13\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA</a>"},{"pid":"1b29be44018fe2399513d08b32cda2a93e8f0a01","tid":953971,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:09:24.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平安夜快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0943dda9c1b1c793b99ee16847f9d67235faf7","tid":953971,"uid":78029,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:10:40.000Z","msg":"補充: <br />\n1. 2016年有篇學術文章出咗「The Bitter Truth About Sugar and Willpower: The Limited Evidential Value of the Glucose Model of Ego Depletion」, 用p-curve analysis 去批評以往19個研究, 指血糖同意志力關係唔大<br />\n<br />\n但之後有另一篇期刊回應, 指眾多研究共識係血糖同腦部運作息息相關, 特別係認知, 而相關研究都話意志力運作腦部位同認知部位相關, 好難排除血糖同認知關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fbfb859507d5cec75e0de91c4d66c0454559060","tid":953971,"uid":62996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:12:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e13d200917e996f833a5ec15f20b74d4c2abaa32","tid":953971,"uid":40718,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:13:33.000Z","msg":"巴打你把聲好似配搞笑片咁 啲停頓位同埋語調好奇怪 同埋啲畫面cut sense可唔可以唔好咁震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467d415df9f01b84df77e61df8942955e1f68345","tid":953971,"uid":78029,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e0943dda9c1b1c793b99ee16847f9d67235faf7","tid":953971,"uid":