es/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163f235ff9b23cc87fad2e0ac17a6d79b076fce1","tid":953971,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:25:15.000Z","msg":"<em>The willpower instinct</em><br />\n教人點用意志力既一本書<br />\n但首先要用意志力睇哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3486ead59bcb285d4676875b3ce214e42af42bd","tid":953971,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f2322a5eaae90bcd7af690f9539f37867b9f79e0","tid":953971,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b63b93e3964272e5440bd8ba8d04afdffc5c50e","tid":953971,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b29be44018fe2399513d08b32cda2a93e8f0a01","tid":953971,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:09:24.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平安夜快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打繼續支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然無直接答你, 但希望今集都幫到你<br />\n平安夜快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果服用葡萄糖supplement對加強意志力有冇用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前睇台灣同馬來西亞嘅youtuber有講到冥想可以改善拖延症<br />\n但我冥想成日都冇耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:35:57.000Z","msg":"葡萄糖係比你補充意志力, 特別係做咗成日野<br />\n<br />\n因為大腦其實都係器官, 都需要用好多能量<br />\n而按質量的比例計算, 大腦佔人體大約2%質量, 但用的能量就接近20%<br />\n大腦認知系統係要用好多血糖, 而意志力亦唔例外<br />\n呢個亦解釋咗點解收工, 肚餓, 訓唔夠會燥, 控制唔到情緒, 唔想郁, 只係想放縱<br />\n<br />\n講到底, 人的心理同生理係有關係, 而處理生理先係因為咁係比較最基本 <br />\n當然心理上, 仲有其他方式, 遲D再講<br />\n<br />\n至於冥想, 係有研究講冥想好多好處式(雖然我抱觀望態度), 其中一個係意志力<br />\n但社會科學實驗都唔係100%, 人同社會等等太複雜, 每個人都會唔同效果<br />\n如果無效就要試吓其他方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e8b1e36b523aacc20a3faba8385781fa4fb0bf","tid":953971,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"163f235ff9b23cc87fad2e0ac17a6d79b076fce1","tid":953971,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:25:15.000Z","msg":"<em>The willpower instinct</em><br />\n教人點用意志力既一本書<br />\n但首先要用意志力睇哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:48:09.000Z","msg":"呢本我有睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果鍾意睇書, 係好享受, 唔洗用意志力迫自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6740ce4e0cef1221eda4e64b3e9a07b3cad4d10","tid":953971,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T13:41:54.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56225ee6994f64d7d583f0db12b4de311735747b","tid":953971,"uid":185162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T21:19:29.000Z","msg":"其實棉花糖個實驗會唔會係證明貪心既小朋友將來會勤力啲讀書同搵到多啲錢...... 愈貪第二粒棉花糖就愈忍得唔食第一粒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主講嘢其實愈來愈進步㗎啦，繼續努力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聖誕快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cd9684b0dd9d2f58aaa88fc5bc6e3f1305c956","tid":953971,"uid":59886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T23:22:48.000Z","msg":"借問聲巴打通常用邊個網搵papers?"},{"pid":"f623dc87450df29167cbb3aa4b166c241c1838da","tid":953971,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T03:08:18.000Z","msg":"頂到十秒頂唔順熄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘩啲手閃嚟閃去暈㗎大佬<br />\n講嘢個tone好唔掂<br />\n練下講嘢先啦，快慢抑揚頓挫都好唔掂"},{"pid":"479d9930af4c7bb8e7a5c1a491ff44574a37843d","tid":953971,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"56225ee6994f64d7d583f0db12b4de311735747b","tid":953971,"uid":185162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T21:19:29.000Z","msg":"其實棉花糖個實驗會唔會係證明貪心既小朋友將來會勤力啲讀書同搵到多啲錢...... 愈貪第二粒棉花糖就愈忍得唔食第一粒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主講嘢其實愈來愈進步㗎啦，繼續努力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聖誕快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:34:10.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打, 聖誕快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我諗每個小朋友都想兩粒, 因為一拎就食的小朋友得好少數<br />\n好多小朋友都係嘗試過忍耐, 但失敗, 研究人員偷望佢地發現有好多方式去忍, 例如用手阻檔自己對眼<br />\n<br />\n如果結合咗最新發現, 係有錢屋企小朋友比較忍得推遲到享受<br />\n階級依然好重要<br />\n<br />\n講嘢就會繼續努力, 仲好努咁調節語速同語調<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e466bc46714566eba02183d63c8ae4330d2fb50f","tid":953971,"uid":78029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91cd9684b0dd9d2f58aaa88fc5bc6e3f1305c956","tid":953971,"uid":59886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T23:22:48.000Z","msg":"借問聲巴打通常用邊個網搵papers?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"大學時會LOGIN咗大學圖書館個網先<br />\n因為好多都比大學買咗<br />\n<br />\n而家用GOOGLE SCHOLAR<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756c4d540e98fa106f9741f0d296e6d5d0b65763","tid":953971,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f623dc87450df29167cbb3aa4b166c241c1838da","tid":953971,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T03:08:18.000Z","msg":"頂到十秒頂唔順熄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘩啲手閃嚟閃去暈㗎大佬<br />\n講嘢個tone好唔掂<br />\n練下講嘢先啦，快慢抑揚頓挫都好唔掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:37:05.000Z","ms